[I] Addons for the Trinity Desktop Environment

[T] tdeaddons contains additional plugins and scripts for some TDE applications.

[U] https://www.trinitydesktop.org/

[A] Trinity Desktop Developers
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/x11
